        <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-chevron-right text-primary me-2"></i><strong>Currency precision</strong>: Multi-tier exchange rate management with configurable decimal precision and historical rate tracking</li>
        <li class="mb-2"><i class="bi bi-chevron-right text-primary me-2"></i><strong>Rule maintenance</strong>: DSL-based fee definitions enabling updates without software deployment cycles</li>
